$ pulumi import proxmoxve:Sdn/subnet:Subnet basic_subnet vnet1/zone1-192.168.1.0-24
```

```sh
$ pulumi import proxmoxve:Sdn/subnet:Subnet dhcp_subnet vnet2/zone2-192.168.2.0-24
```

